Purpose:
BLaDE is a Basic Lambda Dynamics Engine for molecular dynamics based alchemical free energy calculations using multisite lambda dynamics on graphical processor units.

Citation:
Please read and cite the following manuscript when using BLaDE.
Hayes, R. L.; Buckner, J.; Brooks III, C. L.
BLaDE: A Basic Lambda Dynamics Engine for GPU Accelerated Molecular Dynamics Free Energy Calculations
Journal of Chemical Theory and Computation, 2021, 17, 6799-6807
https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acs.jctc.1c00833

Usage:
For installation and usage instructions, see doc/MAIN.txt.
